
= SDL_GetWindowTitle =
Use this function to get the title of a window.


== Syntax ==
```c++
const char* SDL_GetWindowTitle(SDL_Window* window)
```

== Function Parameters ==
{|
|'''window'''
|the window to query
|}

== Return Value ==
Returns the title of the window in UTF-8 format or "" if there is no title.

